& activity
 
 >> Help: Activity (Informational Command)
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Syntax: Activity
 Syntax: Activity/Max
 Syntax: Activity/Con
 
 The 'Activity' command in its various forms shows statistical information
 about the MUX's activity.
 
 - The first form shows a per-hour graph of average people connected.
 - The second form shows the record connected for each hour.
 - The third shows how many players have connected today.
 
